<P>Your comparysons are vne<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">all, because Christ was accused as a brea|ker of the saba<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">th, and his Disciples found fault withall that in hunger did
