<P>MOreouer there was made ma|nifest vnto me, through the same seruice of Loue, and the Lords minister HN. the comming agayne of Christ with his sayntes, and his righteous iudgement, wherein he will iudge the world, with mercye and faythfulnes, and erect agayne his righteousnes, and euen so aco~|plish all, whatsoeuer he hath spo|ken through the mouthes of his
