<DIV2 TYPE="part">
<HEAD>Vitel.</HEAD>
<P>NOw whe~ the Lord of his good|nes, had <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">eleased me out of my blindne<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, and opened mine eyes, th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">~ saw I, that all people vpon earth
