<P>WEre you so relesed of your blind+nes, that you were not subiect to be blind againe? for that is a questio~. were your eyes so opened as <HI>HN.</HI> sayth of himselfe in the pre<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ace of his p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ophesye: the sight of mine eyes be|came clearer then the Christall, and mine vnderstanding brighter then the sunne? <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ou would faine counterfaite your Aucthor in wordes, which be|come neither of you both with your
