<P>WHerein I haue slaundered your Aucthor <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">N.</HI> in supposing him to be chiefe of <HI>Dauid Georges</HI> sect, you show no reason to the contrary: you af|firme that alike we haue slaundered him, and I thinke euen so: For nei|ther of vs haue slaundered him in de<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d, as <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">arre as I can vnderstand: to cleare him of accusation, you onely say all i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> false, what I haue supposed of him: you thinke that is inough among your Familye: for your word among the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> is of some credit: but it be<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">oueth, you
