<P>I hau<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> sayd, y^<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> it is requisit<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, that <HI>HN.</HI> if he will neede<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> haue his new office of a Prophet to be credited, that he must worke miracles&punc; which it se|meth he doeth: as some in your Fami|lye, in sadn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">s haue tould: amongest other matters, this is auouched, that <HI>NH.</HI> is not ignoraunt in any lan|guage, no not the learned tongues,
